==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: pīnmìng sān láng

===Etymology===
Literally: daring third brother
*[[w:Shi Xiu|Shi Xiu]]'s nickname in the ''[[w:Water Margin|Water Margin]]''.  Later used as a [[metaphor]] for someone who is fearless in battle, or an extremely industreous person.[http://www.chinese-tools.com/tools/chinese-dictionary/dico_拼命三郎.html]

